reviewText:
@ALL THE BAD REVIEWS: Do you know you can play every user generated map in toybox for free? You don't need the PlaySets for this. So you can basically play countless hours for free.

All in all, the game looks great, feels great, of course has the original voices in it. The singel parts are a bit pricy, but keep in mind this is meant to be for kids - so getting a kid a 5$ toy to play with is way cheaper than getting a real toy (ot get also the real toy and pay a bit more - or even less if bought used).

The mechanics and game modes are somewhat simple and basic, because this is made with little kids in mind (i guess). but appart from that, you can do, build and combine for endless combinations.
